overview: After Stanley elk escapes from Rivera Asylum, the town in uneasy. They don't know when or where he will strike, but they know that he will. It is only a matter of time. Will the town be able to band together and take care of this menace once and for all? Or will their efforts end in tragedy?
tagline: Stanley Elk has escaped the mental asylum and is on his way into town with one intention...He Comes to Kill
title: HE COMES TO KILL
